{"tid":1045540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子瑜珈失敗露下體 狗狗硬上變「老漢推車」","createTime":"2019-03-03T16:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T02:26:05.000Z","uid":225846,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e32b90dbb63946385f793766e717575da46a7634","tid":1045540,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190303/1526196/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190303%2F1526196%2F&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=99232df8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190303%2F1526196%2F&h=af002b90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190303/1526196/</a><br />\n<br />\n最近歐美網友和中國網友，都瘋傳一段影像，一名女子在戶外做瑜珈，試圖倒立時卻挑戰失敗，但影片的另外一個亮點，在於女子身邊的那隻狗。<br />\n<br />\n當女子在做瑜珈時，這隻狗狗在一旁玩耍，盡顯天真無邪可愛。但當女子倒立失敗倒地時，女子不小心露出下體，這時狗狗突然一陣興奮，直接往女子身上衝去，更形成「老漢推車」的景象，一度變成「老狗推車」。不過最後女子拍拍屁股起身，狗狗也離開了女子。<br />\n<br />\n當網友看到這一段影像，紛紛感到「尷尬」，還有網友認為「真是好狗命」。但也有網友指出，這名女子其實下半身有穿衣物，可能是緊身的肉色內褲或彈性褲，並沒有走光。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"4a84c467c43c52533e8bc9078799e1a3b3bee708","tid":1045540,"uid":136257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14194f402d8532025b64dafaa5825bb8851d081","tid":1045540,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cac5f8ccbd23b9f9115002aac9c2e147e8304dc","tid":1045540,"uid":3820,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"